Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, you've all\Ngiven someone a present, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You wonder if they'll be happy to get it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and you feel like you've\Nput all your feelings into it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my case, it's this stage. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could give all the people\Nwho've come to watch us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and all the companions\Nwho've given it their best with me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a stage that they could smile\Nand say "That was great" about,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would be so awesome! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean... I mean...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a Kaleido Star! Star! Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa aka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
