Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,98...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The daytime practice\Nisn't enough on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nowhere near enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Injured Swan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you overtrain that much,\Nof course it's going to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're trying to force your\Nbody to compensate for the basics you lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're working your feet too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, your center of gravity is unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're controlling that\Nwith the tips of your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These blood blisters are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should really rest\Nyour feet for a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we at least protect the affected\Nparts so you don't put too much weight on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should put balance\Nwork on your training menu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, one, two, three,\None, two, three, one, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one, two, three, one,\Ntwo, three, one, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've got a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What scene will Rosetta be in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean she won't be in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There{\i1} was {\i0}originally a diabolo\Nscene in the script, but she withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a scene Mia put\Nin specifically for Rosetta,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was superfluous\Nto the story, and we cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Sora know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to\Nrethink this configuration again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will everybody please drop this\Nand switch to individual practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the third time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have someone\NI want to introduce to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My feet hurt, but I feel like I'm\Ngetting a better and better grip on this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to practice more and more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll resume your special\Ntraining this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest until I tell you that you can start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, all you gloomy housewives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your gloomy expressions\Nfor your old, tired husbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're with me,\Nshow me your maidenly smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking this knowing\Nthat it won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think there'd be {\i1}some {\i0}training\Ngoods geared toward Sora's problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's got a sharp tongue,\Nbut he's pretty handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's just hard to hate him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is squeaky clean with Clean Finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From your children's doodles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the past doings you\Ncan't tell your husbands about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything's wiped away in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, do a little serious help and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on to the next pile of garbage, Junk Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't garbage, it's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Anna's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't look a thing alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our next treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, that flabby\Nflesh will firm right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's the real Jack Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like work is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The comedy channel has\Nasked me if I'll do a half hour program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be busy, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I refused a request from my beloved\Nsavior, God would be sure to punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna is my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It, like, looks like the\Nlesson is finally going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that a long break?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that means they're close\Nto perfecting the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the final stage of the\Nspecial training for the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change the way I channel\Nmy strength each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sense that and adjust for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's report this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're not going\Nto perform in Swan Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show is an important one for Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't want to get in the\Nway with an unnecessary scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm, how adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But considering your lofty intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you seem to be sneaking around a\Nlot peeking at everybody's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're all right with that, then fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing... The Angel's Maneuver\Nhas really started to take shape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But her balance seems to be\Ngetting worse and worse. Why is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for someone unattractive\Nto play a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the opposite is pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with someone as handsome as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can take anything\Nand push it over the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it will become funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage direction is being\Noutdone by Sora's energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now it's nothing but a nice\Nlittle setup that follows the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who will accept\Nthis kind of textbook construction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the professional critics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:09:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that pose and maintain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver training is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, what do you mean, "over"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver is perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now spend your time until opening\Nday fine-tuning it and resting your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfected?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, I'll keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now? That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you're going to break\Noff the Angel's Maneuver training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at her current level,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would think she can\Nmaintain it for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if she saves her strength,\Nshe can manage the two daily shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really call that the Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's compensating for\Nher lack of basic balance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by forcibly holding the\Nposes with her leg strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense I can't call it the real\Nthing, but the audience won't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she overextends herself, the show will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just think about giving it the widest\Npublicity you can and raking in the profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make good on your\Npromise to your little sister like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?! Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said my special training was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your balance was getting worse,\Nso I thought something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've torn the skin from your toes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've come this far and Leon's\Ngiven you the okay, isn't that enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, it's completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can wake up everybody's\Nangel hearts with a maneuver at this level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special training is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely what Leon said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like, didn't seem to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you're so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the reports of her\Ntraining I've heard up until now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon has minimized balance training{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and spent that time\Nstrengthening her legs instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's trying to modify {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Angel's Maneuver into something\Nshe can do at her current ability level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no way Sora\Nwould accept a fake like that--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something that's only\Nthe appearance of the thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Leon can't completely become\Na demon, there's only one way left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The angel herself has\Nto become a demon, Sora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver is\Ngoing to be changed out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll have\Nto rework the entire stage plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Sora doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're making her get treatment for her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's ripped up the skin of her toes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in this condition she\Ncan't give a proper performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can still go on. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can still do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your feet still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this. I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to try asking Mr. Leon one\Nmore time if he'll continue my training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present from that guy over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken got me a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was looking at catalogues\Nand I just kind of bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't resist, so I bought some too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd recommend it to Leon\Nas a method of improving her balance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while not putting too much\Nof a burden on her feet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided I'm definitely going to\Nask Mr. Leon to continue my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll try recommending this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the special training isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, please continue my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver has been perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now it's all I can do just to\Nsomehow fake the appearance of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't own this maneuver at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that I can give\Neveryone a good time with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say it's over, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll continue\Nmy training by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it until I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I {\i1}will {\i0}master the Angel's\NManeuver before opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So well that I'll get you\Nto acknowledge me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a limit to the amount of pain a\Nperson can put herself through of her own will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously I won't be able\Nto get it right on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I incorporate balance training\Ninto my daily life like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Fool aims for heights yet unseen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you have to get\Ncompletely used to the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, can you get the drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your balance has gotten a lot better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as if the special training\Nisn't over, just as Miss Layla predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can really tell I've been working all my\Nmuscles unnecessarily hard this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now switch legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the feeling of it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I get it this way even without these shoes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your pose slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosetta... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll do balance training\Nagain starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really fired up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be able to do\Nthe Angel's Maneuver as planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's what I mean to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, so that I can\Nget Leon to acknowledge me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do it, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to practice more too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday I'll be onstage\Nwith you on the trapeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I try to force myself to do it on\Nstrength alone, so I can only do 100 reps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my whole body is balanced,\NI should be able to do more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got way more fighting\Nspirit than she's had up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The really hard part is from here on out, Sora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you can't relax your attention to\Nany part of your body, even for an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My whole body is straining... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like one rep is\Ntiring me ten reps' worth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special training is moving backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She like, looks like she's having\Na harder time than she was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sora's started balance training again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after you've learned to fake a technique,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}retraining your body to do\Nit correctly is no easy thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to master the technique {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of instantaneously sensing the\Nflow of my partner's strength soon too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because without that, the\NAngel's Maneuver won't be perfected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is... Sora is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you and Sophie so\Nmerciless toward yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to\Nlet Sora do what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every muscle in your body must\Nbe creaking with overstrain by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep doing this, you'll\Nnever be able to stand onstage again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that happens, I can't\Nshow the audience something fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, are you telling me to\Nshow them something fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With something like that, there's\Nno way the stage without battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the stage without\Nbattles can't become real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fighting all along,\Nwhere Sophie couldn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I struck down those who tried\Nto involve Sophie in their battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, I'm definitely going to become a\Ntrue star and create a stage with no battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure you can do it, Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all's said and done,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never believed in this "stage\Nwith no battles" thing for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that you can't believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because nobody's ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it's like either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly why I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do anything\NI can to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Miss Sophie wanted to see you\Nstanding on a stage without battles, Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me, Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was Sophie's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her goal of becoming a\Ntrue star, and that promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that was all for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie probably knew all\Nabout your fighting and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start the special training again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
