Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:57.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Kaleido Star: New Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like Sora is fighting\Nwith something, doesn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the difference\Nbetween fighting and competing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the difference between hating\Neach other and improving each other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We know why we fight,\Nand why we tackle challenges.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The audience's smiles are\Nwaiting for us! They are! They are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Our Amazing Futures."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
